\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{n}A^{\dagger n}A^{n}=ùïÄ,\quad\sum_{n}B^{n}B^{\dagger n}=ùïÄ
\]

\end_inset

Writing out in full for 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{nk}A_{ik}^{\dagger n}A_{kj}^{n}=\delta_{ij}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
One can think of 
\begin_inset Formula $ùïÄ$
\end_inset

